Wind Walk

An experienced druid may use this spell to gain the
protection of the spirits of wind and storm, allowing
him to walk on the air as though it were solid.  At
higher levels of mastery, the druid can impart this
ability to others.

Command: windwalk <target> (defaults to caster)
Base Cost: 35 SP
Base Recovery: very long
Base Effect: travel (through sky)
Base Duration: medium-long
Guild Level: 15
